1
00:00:00,210 --> 00:00:01,580
That much,
I'm sure of.

2
00:00:02,290 --> 00:00:03,580
She's a superstar.

3
00:00:04,670 --> 00:00:05,920
I'm just a regular guy.

4
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:08,080
She's completely out of my league.

5
00:00:08,750 --> 00:00:10,710
This has nothing to do with
her being a woman and me being a man.

6
00:00:11,250 --> 00:00:12,960
We live in different worlds.

7
00:00:13,830 --> 00:00:16,250
A guy like me,
who's never even been in a relationship...

8
00:00:16,710 --> 00:00:17,960
How am I supposed to be with
someone from a completely different world?

9
00:00:20,460 --> 00:00:21,630
This is for you, as an apology.

10
00:00:23,210 --> 00:00:25,500
It's my fault you got dragged
into all this.

11
00:00:26,790 --> 00:00:28,750
I'll never let something
like that happen again.

12
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:31,170
I'll protect you.

13
00:00:33,210 --> 00:00:34,210
Enough.

14
00:00:34,580 --> 00:00:36,330
Just leave me alone.

15
00:00:37,580 --> 00:00:38,830
You're just making things harder for me.

16
00:00:40,420 --> 00:00:41,960
I get it. You're upset.

17
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:44,420
It's my fault you had to
go through that.

18
00:00:45,580 --> 00:00:46,580
I'm so sorry.

19
00:01:13,500 --> 00:01:14,500
Thank you.

20
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,080
Alright then!
